      <div class="msgContentFrame">If your using zam or yellow grimlin you can just click on the picture of what you need to see the recipe to make that item. Bronze ingot = 5 bronze nuggets, Copper ingot = 5 copper nuggets.  <br /> <br />Bronze nuggets are made by 3 copper ore + 1 tin ore from blacksmiths (makes 12 at a time). Copper nuggets are made from 4 copper ore or 4 yellow copper ore (makes 12 at a time), again the combine is made by smiths.  <br /> <br />I know you can make the copper ones at lv 1 smith and bronze isn't that far off. You can easily get another smith to make them for you but might as well get smithing up because... why not! The ores are found from mining. <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Oct 24th 2010  9:40am by korzek </span></i><div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div><a href="HTTP://www.enjin.com" rel="external nofollow" title="www.enjin.com">[img]<a href="http://sigs.enjin.com/sig-ffxiv/22931_bda9643ac6601722.png" title="http://sigs.enjin.com/sig-ffxiv/22931_bda9643ac6601722.png" rel="external nofollow">http://sigs.enjin.com/sig-ffxiv/22931_bda9643ac6601722.png</a>[/img]</a></div></div>
