      <div class="msgContentFrame">Armorer can't make materials from Ores like the other smithing classes. You're going to have to either level Blacksmith/Goldsmith to be able to smelt your own ore, find somebody to smelt it for you and pay them, or buy the items off of NPC.<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div>~You can do anything once, the trick is to be around to do it again!~ <br /> <br /></div></div>
